{
  "title": "Master Survey Build",
  "showProgressBar": "bottom",
  "pages": [
    {
      "name": "lndgRoot_page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lndgRootPanel",
          "title": "lndgRootPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootHeading",
              "html": "<h2>(lndgRootHeading.h2)About this survey</h2>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootText",
              "html": "<p>(lndgRootText.p)This survey seeks to gather information about how laryngeal paralysis (LarPar, LP) affects the lives of people and the animals they love. It's the first comprehensive survey of its kind and should take no more than ten minutes of your time. We recommend taking the survey on a tablet or desktop, but it works on phones, too. It might just take a little longer.</p> <p>We know how hard it is to lose one's beloved companion. If you're still grieving from the loss, maybe it's best to do the survey later when you've had time to heal. </p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootCrossedOverHeading",
              "html": "<h3>(lndgRootCrossedOverHeading.h3)About your LP companion<h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootCrossedOverText",
              "html": "<p>(lndgRootCrossedOverText.p)If you'd like to continue now, now please tell us your LP companion's name and if your LP companion has crossed over the Rainbow Bridge. This will allow us to personalize the survey to your individual situation.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lndgRootCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "title": "lndgRootCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "lndgRootCmpnName",
                  "title": "(lndgRootCmpnName)Please tell us your companion's name:",
                  "isRequired": true
                },
                {
                  "type": "imagepicker",
                  "name": "lndgRootCrossedOver",
                  "title": "(lndgRootCrossedOver)Has your companion crossed over the Rainbow Bridge?",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "choices": [
                    {
                      "value": "deceased",
                      "imageLink": "./img-companions-rainbow.png",
                      "text": "Crossed over"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "living",
                      "imageLink": "./img-companions.png",
                      "text": "Still with us"
                    }
                  ],
                  "imageWidth": 120,
                  "imageHeight": 120,
                  "showLabel": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootMakeSelection",
              "html": "<p>(lndgRootMakeSelection.p)Once you've made your selection, please choose 'Next' to begin the survey.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lvngRoot_page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngRootPanel",
          "title": "lvngRootPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngRootHeading",
              "html": "<h2>About You(lvngRootHeading.h2)</h2>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngRootText",
              "html": "<p>(lvngRootText.p)We're not asking for your last name, so we have no way to connect you with any of your private data. We believe you're more likely to help us if you feel safe. Click the links below to learn about how your privacy is protected and what we'll be doing with this survey information.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lvngRootAboutSurveyPanel",
              "title": "lvngRootAboutSurveyPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "html",
                  "name": "lvngRootInfoPrivacy",
                  "html": "<div class='srvy-general-info'><img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='srvy-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;<a href='https://example.com' class='srvy-info-link' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>(lvngRootInfoPrivacy)About your privacy</a></div>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "html",
                  "name": "lvngRootInfoYourData",
                  "html": "<div class='srvy-general-info'><img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='srvy-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;<a href='https://example.com' class='srvy-info-link' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>(lvngRootInfoYourData)How will we be using your information?</a></div>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngRootUserText",
              "html": "<p>(lvngRootUserText.p)For verification purposes, we'll contact a random sample of survey particpants, so you may or may not get a message from us. If you're concerned about providing your email address, feel free to use your Facebook account name so we can contact you via Facebook Messenger if need be.</p><p>Your Facebook account name is the part after the Facebook URL. Example: https://www.facebook.com/your.account.name </p><p>With your consent, we may also contact you to talk in more detail about your experience with LP.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "title": "lvngRootAboutUserPanel",
              "name": "lvngRootAboutUserPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "title": "Facebook account or email address:",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserContact",
                  "isRequired": true
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "title": "Your First Name:",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserName",
                  "isRequired": true
                },
                {
                  "type": "boolean",
                  "name": "lvngRootContactOK",
                  "title": "(lvngRootContactOK)May we contact you to talk more about your and {lndgCmpnName}'s experience with laryngeal paralysis?",
                  "isRequired": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "title": "(lvngRootUserAnimalsPanel)About Your Animals",
              "name": "lvngRootUserAnimalsPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "dropdown",
                  "name": "lvngRootAnimalsCount",
                  "title": "(lvngRootAnimalsCount)Including {lndgCmpnName}, how many animals do you have in your care?",
                  "required": true,
                  "choices": [
                    {
                      "value": "1",
                      "text": "One"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "2",
                      "text": "Two"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "3",
                      "text": "Three"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "4",
                      "text": "More than three"
                    }
                  ],
                  "choicesOrder": "none",
                  "otherText": "More than three",
                  "choicesMin": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "boolean",
                  "name": "lvngRootHasInsurance",
                  "required": true,
                  "title": "(lvngRootHasInsurance)Do you have pet insurance for {lndgCmpnName}?"
                },
                {
                  "type": "radiogroup",
                  "name": "lvngRootHasInsuranceOther",
                  "title": "(lvngRootHasInsuranceOther)Do you have pet insurance for your other animals?",
                  "visibleIf": "{lvngRootHasInsurance} = true",
                  "required": true,
                  "choices": [
                    {
                      "value": "1",
                      "text": "No"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "2",
                      "text": "Some, but not all"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "3",
                      "text": "All"
                    }
                  ],
                  "choicesOrder": "none"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lvngCmpn-page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngCmpn-panel",
          "title": "Information Section",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngCmpnAboutCompHeading",
              "html": "<h3>Tell us about your LarPar companion!<h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngCmpnAboutCompText",
              "html": "<p>We're focusing on dogs right now, but if you have a horse or cat with LP, feel free to answer the questions as best as you can. If a question doesn't apply, just leave it blank and skip to the next one.  </p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsSubpanel1",
                  "title": "What is {lndgCompName} name and breed or breed mix?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnName",
                      "title": "Name:",
                      "isRequired": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnBreed",
                      "title": "Breed or mix:",
                      "isRequired": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsSubpanel2",
                  "title": "What is {lndgCompName}'s age (in years and months) and gender?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnAgeYears",
                      "title": "Age in years (number):",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "min": "1",
                      "max": "40",
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 40,
                          "text": "Age must be between 1 and 40"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnAgeMonths",
                      "title": "Months (number 1 - 12)",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "min": 1,
                      "max": 12,
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 12,
                          "text": "Months must be between 1 and 12"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnGender",
                      "title": "Gender:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Female",
                      "labelFalse": "Male"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsSubpanel3",
                  "title": "About how much does {lndgCompName} in pounds or kilos?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnWeight",
                      "title": "Weight (number):",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "min": 1,
                      "max": 2200,
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 2200,
                          "text": "Weight must be between 1 and 2200"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnWeightUnits",
                      "title": "Please choose pounds or kilos:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Kg",
                      "labelFalse": "Lbs"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsSubpanel4",
                  "title": "How energetic, excitable, or anxious is {lndgCompName}? (1=very calm, 5=very excitable)?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "rating",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnExcitable",
                      "title": ""
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "dcsdRoot_page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "dcsdRoot_panel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdRootHeading",
              "html": "<h2>Deceased Page</h2>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdRootText",
              "html": "<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam. Sed nisi. Nulla quis sem at nibh elementum imperdiet. Duis sagittis ipsum.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdRootWhyContact",
              "html": "<img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='survey-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;<a href='https://example.com' class='survey-info-link' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Why provide a contact?</a>"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "dcsdRootUserContact",
              "title": "Facebook account name or email",
              "isRequired": true
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdCmpnAboutHeading",
              "html": "<h3>About your LP companion<h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdCmpnAboutText",
              "html": "<p>We're focusing on dogs right now, but if you have a horse or cat with LP, feel free to answer the questions as best as you can. If a question doesn't apply, just leave it blank and skip to the next one.  </p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "dcsdCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "title": "Companion Details",
              "description": "Please share details about your LP companion here.",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "dcsdCmpnDetailsSubpanel1",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnName",
                      "title": "Name:",
                      "isRequired": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnBreed",
                      "title": "Breed or mix:",
                      "isRequired": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "dcsdCmpnDetailsSubpanel2",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnDOB",
                      "title": "Approximate date of birth:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "inputType": "date"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnGender",
                      "title": "Gender:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Female",
                      "labelFalse": "Male"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "dcsdCmpnDetailsSubpanel3",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnWeight",
                      "title": "Approximate weight (number):",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "inputType": "number"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnWeightUnits",
                      "title": "Please choose pounds or kilos:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Kg",
                      "labelFalse": "Lbs"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}